    /*:.+.*.*:.*..:..*.*:.*..:.+.*.*:*/
    /*                  GENERAL NUMBER UTILITIES                  */
    /*.:.+.*.:*.*.+.:*.*..:.:.*.:*.+.*/

    /// @dev Calculates `floor(a * b / d)` with full precision.
